  <prompt>
Audit 122 found document create profile disposition = Dataverse data fix + UI cosmetic. Root cause: `Save Profile` node (id `c9334fb7-...`) has `sprk_executortype=22` (UpdateRecord) but `sprk_configjson` carries DeliverOutput-shape config (no `entityLogicalName`/`recordId`/`fieldMappings`) — fails `UpdateRecordNodeExecutor.Validate()` on every run. NOT R7 regression, NOT engine bug class.

Primary fix: delete redundant `Save Profile` node OR repair its config. The properly-configured `Update Record` node at execution order 3 already handles PATCH.
  </prompt>

  <role>
You are a Dataverse + Action JPS configuration operator. Apply the surgical fix identified in audit 122; minor UI cosmetic touch if needed.
  </role>

  <goal>
Document create profile wizard works end-to-end. User uploads document → LLM extracts 7 metadata fields → `sprk_document` record is PATCHed with the extracted values → user reviews + saves.
  </goal>

