    - **Preserve Action output schema (operator-tunable surface)** — operators can edit `sprk_outputschemajson` on ACT-011 to add new fields; UI is HARDCODED so adding-new-fields requires code, but EXISTING fields' prompt/temperature remain editable
    - If DELETE path chosen: verify no other consumer depends on `Save Profile` node
